```

### Permission Guard
```typescript
const routes: Routes = [
  {
    path: '',
    component: BookListComponent,
    canActivate: [PermissionGuard],
    data: {
      requiredPolicy: 'BookStore.Books'
    }
  }
];
```

### Programmatic Check
```typescript
